LAGOS  – BetKing is set to sponsor at least eight of its customers to the English Premiership League (EPL) in United Kingdom (UK), which kicks off in the next six weeks. A statement by the company said that the lucky winners would be rewarded with an all-expense paid trip to watch UK , while other customers stand a chance to win exciting prizes in the weeks leading up to the English Premier League. Starting this week till the end of July, the statement hinted that one lucky BetKing customer would win a ticket to watch an EPL match live, while others would win Smart TVs, Smartphones, and N1,000 betting credit in their wallets. It said the EPL pre-season promo is open to new and existing online customers on its platform. Adim Isiakpona, the Chief Operating Officer of KingMakers Nigeria, while speaking on the EPL pre-season promo, said the company was overly excited about the new football season and it wanted to share this excitement with its online customers through the EPL pre-season promo. “We want them to experience that feeling when a new football season starts, the excitement, the rush, that’s BetKing. Commenting on the 2022 FIFA World cup, Adim tells football fans to expect great things from the brand. “If our customers think the EPL pre-season promo is big, wait till they see what we have planned for the 2022 World cup. There’s always more with BetKing,” he added. To qualify to win big in the BetKing EPL promo, new and existing online customers are required to place a bet with a minimum of N500 on either sports or any of the BetKing virtual football leagues, with a minimum number of five selections per ticket, and a minimum of 3.75 odds per coupon. -Advertisement- POLL It however said that terms and conditions apply. The EPL pre-season promo is aimed at rewarding loyal customers who have stayed with the brand during the off-season, the company said. 